1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 27=

3
00:00:45,110 --> 00:00:48,240
So you were worried about him.

4
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:51,280
After all, he's using my body right now.

5
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:52,800
If something happens to him, then I...

6
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,680
Just do it your way.

7
00:01:03,390 --> 00:01:05,280
(I thought my father's power was gone.)

8
00:01:05,430 --> 00:01:07,710
(The Wind and Rain Pavilion
could no longer stir trouble.)

9
00:01:08,310 --> 00:01:09,280
(But things)

10
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,950
(turned out differently
than we expected.)

11
00:01:12,070 --> 00:01:12,920
Ouyang Xun...

12
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:21,350
Never thought

13
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,870
I would end up dying
from poison after all.

14
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,400
Lady Li,

15
00:01:27,510 --> 00:01:28,760
I'll go first.

16
00:01:37,070 --> 00:01:38,310
Ouyang Xun!

17
00:01:38,870 --> 00:01:39,950
Ouyang Xun!

18
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:51,270
Lingsan,

19
00:01:52,790 --> 00:01:53,710
all these years,

20
00:01:54,070 --> 00:01:56,480
how does it feel, being treated
like a killing machine?

21
00:01:59,050 --> 00:02:00,400
Sowing discord between us, are you?

22
00:02:01,790 --> 00:02:03,040
Save your breath.

23
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:05,400
What do you know
about me and the Master?

24
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,040
He almost killed you.

25
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:09,370
And yet you still treat him like this.

26
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:12,150
Dying for him

27
00:02:12,630 --> 00:02:14,520
would be my best ending.

28
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,360
Shiyi once thought the same way.

29
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,360
But now,

30
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,800
he's chosen to live for himself.

31
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:29,080
Stop wasting words with them.

32
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,750
End this quickly.

33
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,910
You're about to die,

34
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,190
yet you still talk so much.

35
00:02:44,610 --> 00:02:45,850
Your timing couldn't be better.

36
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,360
Every kill counts as a gain.

37
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,680
Avenge me.

38
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,630
Go! Hurry and leave!

39
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:30,870
Why didn't you strike sooner?

40
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,960
My duty is to protect Her Highness.

41
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:36,750
The lives of others have nothing
to do with me.

42
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:43,920
Qingyao.

43
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,000
You've returned.

44
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,120
The two great masters of the Pavilion

45
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,750
were beyond my expectations.

46
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:52,000
If Eunuch Leng

47
00:03:52,010 --> 00:03:53,400
had made his move earlier,

48
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,240
then Ouyang Xun

49
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,150
might not have had to die.

50
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,280
I will remember them.

51
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,310
What

52
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:11,190
do they mean to you?

53
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,080
A group of capable subordinates.

54
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,040
And what about Gu Qingyao?

55
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,880
How dare you!

56
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,700
Do you even know who you're speaking to?

57
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,920
Qingyao, your place in my heart,

58
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,830
comes only after the realm.

59
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:08,630
(After His Majesty passed away,)

60
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,920
(Ling Yu ascended the throne
as he had wished.)

61
00:05:50,260 --> 00:05:52,550
(Noble Consort Xiao took her own life
in the Cold Palace.)

62
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:54,310
(And the guard named Wu Yun)

63
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:55,560
(vanished without a trace.)

64
00:05:58,820 --> 00:06:03,700
(Prime Minister's Residence)

65
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:06,430
(Minister Gu resigned, citing illness,)

66
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:07,750
(and returned to his hometown.)

67
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:11,800
(Ling Yu spared his life in the end.)

68
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,830
Keeping his life

69
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:14,390
is already a blessing.

70
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:19,800
His Majesty cares for you.

71
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:24,480
He clearly cares more about the realm.

72
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:36,000
It was wise not to wipe them all out.

73
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:40,000
Though the Wind and Rain Pavilion
has fallen,

74
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:41,630
some still slipped away.

75
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,870
If those people target him,

76
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:46,760
it will be troublesome.

77
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,920
He seems

78
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,920
always to see farther than us.

79
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,750
Only in this way

80
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:57,240
can one be a true wise ruler.

81
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,750
But I always feel

82
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,560
that I can't see through him.

83
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:09,480
Perhaps marrying me

84
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,190
was just another move in his plan.

85
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:17,190
Father used me as a bargaining chip

86
00:08:17,190 --> 00:08:18,290
to divert others' attention.

87
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,600
Isn't Ling Yu

88
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,600
also using the marriage alliance

89
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,240
to strengthen his position

90
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,950
as Crown Prince?

91
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,080
Stop overthinking.

92
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:37,600
No matter what, it's all over now.

93
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,800
Yes,

94
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,120
it's all over.

95
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,360
It's just a pity that Wu Yun got away.

96
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,650
The celestial stone on him

97
00:08:55,650 --> 00:08:56,770
has vanished without a trace.

98
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,510
Otherwise, we could have swapped bodies.

99
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,200
Swapped bodies?

100
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,270
Then what?

101
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,440
Once we've swapped bodies,

102
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:21,550
you'll return to being the Empress,

103
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,870
and I'll roam free as a wanderer.

104
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,510
Empress?

105
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:29,390
Mm.

106
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,240
Isn't this what you've always
dreamed of?

107
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,670
To be the Empress,

108
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,510
above all others.

109
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:39,670
Is it?

110
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,360
It's what I once longed for.

111
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:49,800
No.

112
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,870
This is not the life I want.

113
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,360
Intrigue and scheming,

114
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,120
plots and deception,

115
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:01,140
all for the sake of power,

116
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:02,350
turning against one's own kin,

117
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:04,360
living every day in constant fear,

118
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,790
with life and death
in another's control,

119
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,000
resorting to every possible means...

120
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:12,360
The Imperial Palace

121
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,240
is clearly the most terrifying prison

122
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,510
in the world.

123
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:19,720
I don't want it.

124
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:23,750
I really don't.

125
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,560
Qingyao.

126
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,600
No matter what you decide,

127
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,390
I'll stand by you.

128
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:03,390
But Ling Yu...

129
00:11:04,790 --> 00:11:06,030
What if he refuses to let me go?

130
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:10,440
That's easy.

131
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,480
If he doesn't let you go,

132
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,150
then at worst,

133
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,240
I'll stab him again.

134
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,240
But now,

135
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,960
he's the Emperor,

136
00:11:23,790 --> 00:11:25,390
surrounded by countless masters.

137
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,800
You might fail.

138
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:28,790
That's even simpler.

139
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:30,600
If I can't stab him,

140
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:32,120
I should at least scare him.

141
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:34,390
I want to make sure he can't sleep well

142
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:35,440
and can't eat well.

143
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,200
After some time,

144
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:38,750
he's bound to yield.

145
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,360
In that case, that Emperor

146
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,200
will truly be in disgrace.

147
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:15,790
Lingyi,

148
00:12:16,450 --> 00:12:18,030
you really never give up your scheming.

149
00:12:20,030 --> 00:12:21,670
Even if I become a spirit,

150
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:26,080
I'll never let you go.

151
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:28,720
You vile scorpion!

152
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,500
Lingsan was slain by Leng Wuchang.

153
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:32,700
If you seek revenge, find him.

154
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:33,480
Why come after us?

155
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:34,380
Silence!

156
00:12:36,270 --> 00:12:37,910
If you hadn't betrayed us,

157
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:41,390
Lingsan would still be alive.

158
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:45,480
Had we stood together,

159
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,790
the Master's grand plan
would have succeeded.

160
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:50,550
All of this happened because of you.

161
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,030
You're not just arrogant,

162
00:12:52,030 --> 00:12:53,000
but also terribly naive.

163
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:55,650
The Wind and Rain Pavilion
you think so highly of

164
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,620
is nothing at all

165
00:12:56,620 --> 00:12:57,990
in the eyes of the Imperial Court.

166
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:03,600
Since ancient times,

167
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:07,000
victors are crowned as kings.

168
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,270
You won this time,

169
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,750
so naturally you can say
whatever you want.

170
00:13:14,390 --> 00:13:16,000
But I really want to know

171
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:19,910
whether you so-called superior people

172
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,270
actually bleed.

173
00:14:03,610 --> 00:14:06,210
♪When a breeze passes by♪

174
00:14:06,730 --> 00:14:10,050
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

175
00:14:10,050 --> 00:14:12,690
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

176
00:14:13,010 --> 00:14:16,170
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

177
00:14:16,530 --> 00:14:19,490
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

178
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:22,810
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

179
00:14:23,010 --> 00:14:25,730
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

180
00:14:25,890 --> 00:14:29,530
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

181
00:14:29,690 --> 00:14:31,290
♪I finally understood that truth♪

182
00:14:31,290 --> 00:14:32,770
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

183
00:14:32,970 --> 00:14:34,610
♪I lose my way in the night♪

184
00:14:34,610 --> 00:14:36,090
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

185
00:14:36,090 --> 00:14:37,770
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

186
00:14:37,770 --> 00:14:40,730
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

187
00:14:41,170 --> 00:14:43,610
♪For you and me to meet again♪

188
00:14:44,050 --> 00:14:46,890
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

189
00:14:47,170 --> 00:14:49,250
♪In the pouring rain♪

190
00:14:49,250 --> 00:14:53,610
♪As if you are still by my side♪
